%Docstring
Returns ``True`` if the given ``fileName`` matches a file ``filter`` string.

E.g a filter of "GeoTIFF Files (*.tiff *.tif)" would return ``True`` for a ``fileName``
of "/home/test.tif", or ``False`` for "/home/test.jpg".

.. versionadded:: 3.18
%End

